title: Provides for procedure for election of Speaker
fulltext:
ASSEMBLY  RESOLUTION providing for the procedure for the election of the
Speaker

RESOLVED, That the House do now proceed to the election of Speaker for a
term of two years, that the roll of the members be called by the  Acting
Clerk,  and  that  each  member,  as his/her name is called, openly name
his/her choice for such office.
